OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold but bright start to the
OL,6,Fday, with sunny spells. Becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy into the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith a chance of isolated showers.
OL,9,FLight winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers soon easing this
OL,12,Fevening with partly cloudy skies.
OL,13,FCloudier for a time overnight with a
OL,14,Fchance of some outbreaks of light
OL,15,Frain. Becoming breezy and cool.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA dry and sunny day with only
OL,18,Fa little patchy cloud, mainly in the
OL,19,Fmorning. Becoming increasingly breezy,
OL,20,Fparticularly over hills. Cloud may
OL,21,Fincrease overnight from the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
