OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith variable amounts of cloud
OL,7,FWednesday to Friday, though
OL,8,Fincreasingly sunny each afternoon as
OL,9,Fcloud burns back to coasts. Breezy,
OL,10,Fparticularly over hills. Mild, cooler
OL,11,Fnear coasts.
